---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Mental Health Support | Veteran Support Services"
  description="Explore mental health support services available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Learn about PTSD treatment, counselling, and other resources.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Mental Health Support for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) recognises the importance of mental health support for veterans. This page outlines the various mental health services and resources available to help you manage service-related mental health conditions.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">PTSD Treatment Programmes</h2>
        <p>Specialised treatment for Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD) includes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Trauma-focused Cognitive Behavioural Therapy (CBT)</li>
          <li>Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing (EMDR) therapy</li>
          <li>Group therapy sessions with fellow veterans</li>
          <li>Residential treatment programmes for severe cases</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Counselling and Therapy Services</h2>
        <p>A range of counselling and therapy options are available:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>One-on-one counselling with trained therapists</li>
          <li>Couples and family therapy to address relationship issues</li>
          <li>Cognitive Behavioural Therapy for anxiety and depression</li>
          <li>Mindfulness and relaxation techniques</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Substance Abuse Support</h2>
        <p>For veterans struggling with substance abuse, we offer:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Detoxification programmes</li>
          <li>Rehabilitation services</li>
          <li>Ongoing support groups</li>
          <li>Dual diagnosis treatment for co-occurring mental health issues</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Peer Support Networks</h2>
        <p>Connecting with fellow veterans can be a valuable part of recovery:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Peer-led support groups</li>
          <li>Mentoring programmes</li>
          <li>Online forums and communities</li>
          <li>Social events and activities</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Crisis Support</h2>
        <p>For immediate mental health crises, we provide:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>24/7 crisis helpline</li>
          <li>Emergency mental health services</li>
          <li>Suicide prevention support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/support/career-transition" class="text-decoration-none">Career Transition Support</a></li>
              <li><a href="/medical/rehabilitation" class="text-decoration-none">Rehabilitation Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="/compensation/disability-pensions" class="text-decoration-none">Disability Pensions</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Mental Health Helpline</h3>
            <p>If you're struggling, don't hesitate to reach out. Our helpline is available 24/7.</p>
            <p class="fw-bold">0800 XXX XXXX</p>
            <a href="/mental-health-support" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
